title: Sharpen Your Kitchen Knife Like A Master Sharpener
description:
By the end of this video my hope is you will be able to go home, get your first set of whetstones, and be able to start your journey in the world of sharpening your own knives. Welcome to sharp boi hours. 

Thank you to Bernal Cutlery find them here: https://bernalcutlery.com/
Whetstones used in the video: https://bernal-cutlery.shoplightspeed.com/sharpening-supplies/whetstones-manmade/
